OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSri Lanka gives government 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fworkers extra day off a    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fweek                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sri Lanka is giving government         
OL,6, officials an extra day off a week to   
OL,7, encourage them to grow food, amid fears
OL,8, of a food shortage.                    
OL,10,FThe country has around one million     
OL,11,Fpublic sector employees.               
OL,13,FIt comes as the island nation, home to 
OL,14,Faround 22 million, faces its worst     
OL,15,Feconomic crisis in more than 70 years. 
OL,17,FSri Lanka is struggling to pay for     
OL,18,Fcritical imports such as food, fuel and
OL,19,Fmedicine as it faces a severe shortage 
OL,20,Fof foreign currencies.                 
